textAfterTable: Highlights: Enjoy the ultimate in personal service on the m/v Tere Moana; with one crew member for every 1.5 guests, you're assured the highest level of personal attention. Indulge in delicious French cuisine with a Polynesian accent at L’Etoile, or enjoy breakfast or lunch indoors or al fresco at La Veranda. Pamper yourself at the award-winning luxury Deep Nature Spa by Algotherm or hop aboard a windsurfer. Savor a glass of fine wine while listening to live music at Le Salon or attend a stimulating onboard lecture. Your Package Includes: Your package includes oceanview accommodations, all onboard gratuities, onboard meals, most beverages (excludes premium liquor and wine), 24-hour room service, refrigerator replenished daily, in-suite setup and butler service in categories B and above, and port charges. It does not include government fees, taxes, fuel supplements, or personal expenses. View more
